item.title: Shifting Through The Maze Of Offers – Christine McIver
item.description: Inspired Choices for Business Growth with Christine McIver As an entrepreneur, the number of offers, services, and strategies available can feel overwhelming. In this episode of Inspired Choices for Business Growth, Christine McIver helps you cut through the noise and focus on the offers that truly align with your business goals. She’ll guide you in evaluating opportunities that can fuel your growth while avoiding distractions that can slow you down... Feed: https://www.inspiredchoicesnetwork.com/xml-feed/?id=16891
